---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Sidebar from '../../components/Sidebar.astro';
const title = "AGN Feedback in Abell 119 - ArXiv Atlas";
---
<Base title={title}>
  <Sidebar />
  <main class="page-main">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>AGN Feedback in Galaxy Clusters: A Multi-wavelength Study of Abell 119</h1>
      <div class="page-meta">
        <span class="tag">arXiv:2603.09905</span>
        <span class="tag">2026-03-11</span>
        <span class="tag">astro-ph.GA</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <h2 id="section-0">Overview</h2>
      <p>
        Multi-wavelength analysis of AGN feedback in galaxy cluster Abell 119 using Chandra X-ray, VLA radio, and SDSS optical data.
      </p>

      <h2 id="section-1">Key Findings</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Three generations</strong> of X-ray cavities (ages 10-100 Myr)</li>
        <li><strong>Episodic AGN activity</strong> with duty cycle ~10%</li>
        <li><strong>Total mechanical energy</strong>: ~10^61 erg injected into ICM</li>
        <li>Sufficient to offset radiative cooling in cluster core</li>
        <li>Uplifted cool gas in cavity wakes with metallicity enhancements</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="section-2">Relevance to Galaxy Evolution</h2>
      <p>
        AGN feedback offsets cooling in cluster cores and transports enriched material. Episodic activity maintains long-term heating of the intracluster medium.
      </p>

      <h2 id="section-3">Concepts</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/concepts/agn-feedback">AGN feedback</a></li>
        <li><a href="/concepts/x-ray-cavities">X-ray cavities</a></li>
        <li><a href="/concepts/cluster-cooling">Cluster cooling</a></li>
        <li><a href="/concepts/bcg-evolution">BCG evolution</a></li>
      </ul>

      <div class="references">
        <h2 id="section-4">Citation</h2>
        <pre><code>@article&#123;zhang2026agn,&#125;
  title=&#123;AGN Feedback in Galaxy Clusters: Abell 119&#125;,
  author=&#123;Zhang, H. and others&#125;,
  journal=&#123;arXiv:2603.09905&#125;,
  year=&#123;2026&#125;
&#125;</code></pre>
      </div>

      <p><a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2603.09905" target="_blank">View on arXiv →</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
